<plot>Redemption, second chances, and the healing power of love are the themes in the COMPLETELY SUNG musical extravaganza "Art Thief Musical!" A sexy, cat-suit-wearing burglar named Clarity meets and falls in love at first sight, with a lonely museum custodian Salvation. Fate brings them together, but do they possess the strength to take it to the next step? They've made their choices in life, but are they bound by the repercussions of those choices? She is wanted by the police. He has nothing to give her. But somehow it all ends up okay...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?046402</url></doc>
